    // Command parsing (client-side UI open triggers)
    // Vietnamese command patterns: "má»Ÿ dá»‹ch vá»¥", "má»Ÿ phÃ²ng", "má»Ÿ tiá»‡n nghi", "má»Ÿ Ä‘Ã¡nh giÃ¡", "má»Ÿ khuyáº¿n mÃ£i", "má»Ÿ Ä‘áº·t phÃ²ng", etc.
